add a new Modifier Weak Point Strike
Every time Daisho crit any enemys, they will suffer from 1 random debuff out of 2 that will only affect Daisho him-self or his spells
DEBUFF 1 Enemys will take 12% more damage from BladeStorm and will have reduce healing by 8%, if Daisho damage them with BladeStorm,
it will have 65% chance to increase the duration of BladeStorm by 0.1 every time they get damage by it. DEBUFF 2 enemys will take 35%
more damage from Wind Walk and if Daisho land a True Strike on them, they will take 70% more damage instead and get stun longer for 0.6
second and bleed for 17 plus 0.4% of their max health in pure damage for 3 seconds. The Weak Point Strike debuff last 4 second and
enemys that got Weak Point Strike cannot get it again for 13 seconds and a Symbol will spawn on their head Showing witch one of the
Debuff they are affected by.

